      <title>投资者称工党获胜后英国资产重获青睐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-assets-are-back-in-favor-after-labour-victory-investors-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默领导的工党在选举中取得压倒性胜利后，英国资产重新受到青睐，这让人们希望英国能迎来一段政治平静时期，并稳定国家财政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-assets-are-back-in-favor-after-labour-victory-investors-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 08:40:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞驳斥民意调查称极右翼未能在法国占据多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/le-pen-rejects-polls-showing-far-right-short-of-french-majority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞否认了有关她所在的极右翼国民联盟党在法国立法选举中无法获得绝对多数的预测，并警告说，如果她得不到执政授权，她将陷入“泥潭”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/le-pen-rejects-polls-showing-far-right-short-of-french-majority</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 07:20:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党大选获胜，英国国内股市今年涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-stocks-lead-europe-rally-on-labour-s-landslide-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党在选举中取得压倒性胜利，激发了人们对政治稳定可能支持经济增长反弹的希望，与英国国内经济相关的股票今年涨幅最大。欧洲股市也普遍上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-stocks-lead-europe-rally-on-labour-s-landslide-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 07:09:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师称中国人民银行对债券市场的打击将收效甚微</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-salvo-on-bond-rally-may-have-limited-impact-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管央行准备出售数千亿元人民币的债券以冷却股市上涨，但中国观察人士对央行影响收益率下行压力的能力仍表示怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-salvo-on-bond-rally-may-have-limited-impact-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:04:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
